messages.messageBody:
http://sandradodd.com/moonflowers

I couldn't get all fifteen in one photo. <g>

THANKS whoever knew about the spider lilly. Blades are coming up. I moved
it. There was a single bulb, but it was big and rooty. <g> Maye it will
split next year.

Yes, I should be asleep. I dibsed the bed in the back of the van, and have
been up doing last-minute trip preparation, like, uh... taking and posting
photos of our record number of moonflowers. We're going to miss some big
nights, but when we get back they should still be there.

I hope I sleep to Oklahoma, but I might only make Texas.

Sandra
